data.description: Exclusive Offer: $2,000 Agent Bonus! Plus, Enjoy a 1% Preferred Lender Credit and Free Seller Rate Buy Down. Builder's 10-Year Warranty Included. Move-In Ready!  Discover the epitome of modern living in this meticulously maintained 1,619 square foot home, surpassing the allure of new constructions with its plethora of custom upgrades. From the moment you arrive, the charm of the well-manicured front yard and inviting porch sets the tone for a lifestyle of comfort and elegance.  Step inside to experience the seamless blend of sophistication and functionality, showcased by the expansive layout adorned with crown molding, tasteful neutral paint, and luxurious laminate flooring. The attention to detail is evident at every turn, including the immaculate epoxy garage floors and the convenience of having a washer and dryer already included.    Embrace the eco-friendly benefits of solar panels, ensuring sustainable living while significantly reducing energy costs. This residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, offering ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. The heart of the home, a stunning granite countertop kitchen, features top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including a stylish double door fridge.    Indulge your culinary desires in this chef's haven, complete with additional cabinets, sleek cabinet handles, and a tasteful backsplash. The open-concept living area seamlessly flows into the kitchen, fostering an ideal environment for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories.  Escape to the tranquility of the backyard oasis, where a covered patio and expansive, level lot beckon for outdoor enjoyment and endless possibilities for landscaping. Nestled in a coveted San Antonio neighborhood, this property offers convenient access to schools, parks, shopping centers, grocery stores, and major transportation routes.  Don't let this opportunity pass you by. Schedule a viewing today and experience the unparalleled comfort and convenience awaiting you at 5831 Rolling Glen. Make this remarkable property your forever home.
